ories. These articles go hand in hand with slowing down the design process! As well as these goodies, there is a great website example, an article on web performance ethics, and more in this weeks [&hellip;]</p>\n","featured_media":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.829268292682927,"src":"/static/526ed1f19e7f57a5f034bf1e1269a76c/3b7c4/User-Journey-Mapping.jpg","srcSet":"/static/526ed1f19e7f57a5f034bf1e1269a76c/03841/User-Journey-Mapping.jpg 250w,\n/static/526ed1f19e7f57a5f034bf1e1269a76c/26396/User-Journey-Mapping.jpg 500w,\n/static/526ed1f19e7f57a5f034bf1e1269a76c/3b7c4/User-Journey-Mapping.jpg 750w","sizes":"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px"}}}},"categories":[{"name":"Coding"},{"name":"Creative"},{"name":"Design"},{"name":"General Coding"},{"name":"Inspiration"},{"name":"Ramblings"},{"name":"UX"},{"name":"Weekly Rundown"}],"tags":[{"name":"Copy"},{"name":"Design"},{"name":"Design System"},{"name":"Features"},{"name":"Framework"},{"name":"interface"},{"name":"Interfaces"},{"name":"Journey Mapping"},{"name":"JS"},{"name":"Storytelling"},{"name":"Teaching"},{"name":"Trends"},{"name":"User Flow"},{"name":"User Journey"},{"name":"UX"}]}},{"node":{"id":"6383ffcf-da2c-50ae-9736-fc41cff44b93","slug":"creative-development-inspiration-58","template":"","format":"standard","title":"Creative / Development Inspiration 58","date":"2019-01-14T08:07:04.000Z","excerpt":"<p>New year happened. and then Christmas happened. And then I went away for jolly. Enough time to break a habit. &nbsp; Not a chance. &nbsp; This weeks design and developer inspiration rundown has even more of the good stuff. Want to know more about accessibility? Check. How about the newest CMSs on the scene? I [&hellip;]</p>\n","featured_media":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.829268292682927,"src":"/static/2d2fea739405c49494eb7acc38afa09f/3b7c4/story-mapping.jpg","srcSet":"/static/2d2fea739405c494